domestic violence relationship, coming up here to try to get some

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:14.680
space from her ex partner. Due to the nature of her

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:19.260
alcohol use disorder, she ended up... We ended up doing a wellness check,

00:03:19.420 --> 00:03:22.720
